      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dependable daily driver who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few scuffs on the rear bumper. The interior is clean but has some minor wear on the driver's seat upholstery. It has been regularly maintained and is ready for the road, offering a solid driving experience at a reasonable price point.",
