    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom-quality condition, exhibiting no discernible wear or mechanical compromise. Every aspect of this automobile reflects meticulous stewardship, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original manufacture. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly flawless asset.",
