    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person! Honestly, it\u2019s like stepping back in time\u2014this car is in absolutely incredible shape and looks like it just left the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept, so the paint is glowing and the interior is spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
