    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a benchmark for naturally aspirated performance. This S54-powered coupe features a 3.2L straight-six with factory-spec compression and razor-sharp individual throttle body response. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system overhauled with uprated components to ensure mechanical longevity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise engagement, while the variable M differential lock delivers optimal torque distribution. The exterior retains its original factory clear coat with no evidence of panel misalignment or oxidation. This is a meticulously preserved, collector-grade example for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
