    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered since day one. It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom\u2014honestly, it's in flawless shape! I\u2019m only parting with it because I\u2019m downsizing, and I\u2019d love for it to go to a home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It\u2019s a total dream to drive, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll fall in love with it the second you hop in. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look! \u2728",
