    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-grade 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This specimen maintains factory-spec tolerances with a documented VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains perfectly rigid, utilizing its original aluminum control arms and a precision-tuned multi-link rear suspension with zero bushing play. Clad in original paint with an immaculate interior, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated high-revving engineering.",
